∞Stranger Stop Here and Rest Your Thoughts on
LOVELY LISA GRAYLEY
Mum to Pretty Lottie, Sweetheart to Paul and Beautiful Friend to
Those of Us Who Knew Her "Sweet Dreams Sis""≥
∞This bench and nearby tree
stands in honour of the legendary actor
Jeremy Brett
(1933-1995)
His love, laughter and immense courage
in the face of adversity inspires us all"∏
µAdele (Estelle) Kruger 1941-2008
In loving memory of our mother, grandmother and best friend
We shall never forget the endless love you gave us
And your total devotion to animals"∏
µEve Louise Boundy
15th July 2014
If ever there is tomorrow when we're not together...there is something you
must always remember. You are braver than you believe, stronger than you
seem and smarter than you think. But the most important thing is
even if we're apart... I'll always be with you
A.A. Milne"æ
ªin Loving Memory of the "Three Bearham Sisters"
Ellen: 09.11.1913  02.05.2013
Rose: 18.01.1920  30.11.2012
Lillian: 13.04.1918  08.01.2000
Who Spent Many Happy Hours in Battersea Park"ø
ºTom and Iris Gill
21 Aug 1933-18 Jan 2019 19 June 1933-10 Dec 1992
Beloved Mum, Dad, Grandad. Sharing walks & smiles together.
Enjoying music, theatre, family & a pint (or two!) for Tom"ø
